{"type": "article", "id": 6932, "title": "蓝黑or白金？又一个热门话题成了品牌们营销的战场", "description": "一个热门话题走红的速度越来越快了，过气的速度也是。", "date": "2015-02-28T15:53:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7345, "name": "The Dress"}, {"id": 65, "name": "营销"}], "category": 18, "column": null, "author": 3926, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605213825OhbuGlQm0Je5fv9k.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如果你刚刚来到地球，可能很难理解昨天在全世界的互联网上发生了什么。人们为一条难看的裙子到底是什么颜色大打出手，夫妻反目，甚至连见面打招呼的方式也变成了“蓝黑还是白金？”\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t事情起源于这张你可能已经看吐了的图片，而后随着 Taylor Swift 等名人的转发迅速发酵。毕竟，不是每一条裙子都有机会被叫做“#The Dress”的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213815AGJSlgpio5Xe9hUQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213815OnJmZF1IG97Hjgsu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t不少品牌在社交网络上跃跃欲试地做起了营销：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052138161jqcHove7J8ipQW3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213817tAhY7gX6Qm8NnpVO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t饿了就吃士力架？能为一条裙子痴狂成这样，看来互联网也是饿了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213817bYd56NifB4jCVLKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213817RojzLK0icWbIfs1r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052138182YLlFGbDcPpWv8Ax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.253125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213819TJMCR1VZwqfy0IlY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t还有这种两个品牌打情骂俏的：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213820IKLS09nrcqpgv7kD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213820z3vBxWAgIKphGMes.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213821YSmjplH90fLuv4q8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t“为什么大家都叫我们 Gold 和 White？”M&amp;M 问出了很多人心底的问题：互联网君，你肿么了？！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213822NIzafK9u2AZJo4Qg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t相比之下，在国内的社交网络上，能迅速反应过来并利用这个话题做营销的品牌就少了很多。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213822XRHnv23BMl6jay5O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213822q4FOVn6oe0y7mhwx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213823gzBhU1vbcfI5eyRt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213823NPvlgZCnhSkOBwT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t更多的是段子手们的作品，比如\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213824YdwUFsqAjL68GyHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.18125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213824HmGEutJYZvdbai7V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.253125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052138251Hm9AaDUlu2ICwFX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.2546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t一场喧嚣过后，如果还有人不知道变色原理的话，可以看果壳的这篇<a href=\"http://www.guokr.com/article/439985/\" target=\"_blank\">科普文章</a>。\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}